{"tid":1783694,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「靜雞雞靜靜雞靜靜靜雞雞雞」嘅真正用途以及當前氣氛低迷解決方法","createTime":"2019-12-15T05:30:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T17:51:09.000Z","uid":263933,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5ba0a5f8861c823c0cd2635962265ce89ce7181d","tid":1783694,"uid":263933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T05:30:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">話地下化話靜靜雞係叫勇武做，唔係你班和理非都要靜呀!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n唔該和理非繼續保持團火，聖誕節唔好留係屋企，出哂嚟去邊都得，咩呀唔比過聖誕呀?一向聖誕都多人!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">抗爭低迷就去打經濟戰</span></span>，揾黃色小店齊齊帶動，唔好淨係幫襯出名個啲；<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">揀禮物送比還押手足同無家可歸嘅手足。</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">出嚟唱歌、派靚靚文宣，繼續平安夜倒數除夕倒數。</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">隨口講都幾多嘢可以做，唔好再等人發號施令，自己揾嘢搞，半年啦可以出嘅和理非活動基本都出哂，橋唔怕舊最緊要受。做嘢啦手足。</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3f2d40490f3eb4586f4aecc5dd495535c3856df","tid":1783694,"uid":278886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T05:33:09.000Z","msg":"push merry christmas"},{"pid":"bcc2b8dcc887f12b4c75ab148c8617648cd10ab3","tid":1783694,"uid":263933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T05:35:22.000Z"